 but it was playable.  If I needed more performance I can lower it even more.<br>
<br>
So give the computer industry a year and half/2 years and EQ2 will probably run just fine.<br>
<br>
Oh yeah, and EQ is a terrible game to get an idea of how a game should run.<br>
